Man wants ex-wife back for Valentine’s Day
2012-02-15 01:22:37 GMT
BEIJING, Feb. 15 (Xinhuanet) --A man surnamed Liu in Dalian, Northeast China's Liaoning province seeks to remarry his ex-wife after cutting off her hair, Liaoshen Evening News reported.Liu suspected his wife kept the long hair to attract or flirt with other man behind his back. So hecut off her hair while she was asleep three years ago. The wife, who also suffered domestic violence when Liu was drunk, later filed divorce.Liu regretted the divorce and asked several times for a reunion with his wife. However, the wifesaid it will take time to regain her trust and only agreed to a dinner on Valentine’s Day.(Source: China Daily)
